17
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:51.080
Wu Tai, don’t do this!

18
00:00:55.140 --> 00:00:56.480
Lianlian, you can sleep with other

19
00:00:56.480 --> 00:00:57.200
men,

20
00:00:57.380 --> 00:00:58.240
