29
00:01:12.140 --> 00:01:13.560
So you put on this act for me,

30
00:01:13.820 --> 00:01:14.580
just to make me agree

31
00:01:14.580 --> 00:01:15.740
to break up with you,

32
00:01:16.020 --> 00:01:16.380
